# Mint Rail Products — Environment Configuration
# Copy to .env and fill in values.

# ── AI Backend (choose one) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Option 1: Local Kwyre inference (local-first, no cloud dependency)
# Start Kwyre server first: python server/serve_local_4bit.py
# KWYRE_API_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000
# KWYRE_API_KEY=sk-kwyre-dev-local

# Option 2: Anthropic Claude API (cloud)
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# If both are set, KWYRE_API_URL takes priority (local-first).

# ── Product Server ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# All products default to port 8000.
# Run with: uvicorn server.app:app --reload
# Or:       uvicorn server.app:app --host 0.0.0.0 --reload
